phyConsole.name: phyConsole
phyConsole.contactinfo: Postal: Zhone Technologies, Inc. @ Zhone Way 7001 Oakport Street Oakland, CA 94621 USA Toll-Free: +1 877-ZHONE20 (+1 877-946-6320) Tel: +1-510-777-7000 Fax: +1-510-777-7001 E-mail: support@zhone.com
phyConsole.description: The Zhone console mib that applies to the console connection to an Information Services card. There is only one supported connection at a time, thus the single instance implementation.

consoleHeight.name: consoleHeight
consoleHeight.description: The height of the console in the number of lines displayed. The default value is 24.

consoleCurrentUser.name: consoleCurrentUser
consoleCurrentUser.description: The name of the current or last user logged in to the system.

consoleLastLoginTime.name: consoleLastLoginTime
consoleLastLoginTime.description: Time at which the last user logged in. If a user has never logged in on this system, the value returned is 0. This is the sysuptime value as defined in rfc1907.

consoleLastLogoutTime.name: consoleLastLogoutTime
consoleLastLogoutTime.description: The sysuptime at which the last user logged out. A value of 0 is returned if a logout has never occured OR if a user is currently logged in.

consoleCharsOut.name: consoleCharsOut
consoleCharsOut.description: The number of characters sent by the console since initialization.

consoleCharsIn.name: consoleCharsIn
consoleCharsIn.description: The number of charcters received by the console since initialization.

consoleBaudRate.name: consoleBaudRate
consoleBaudRate.description: The speed of the console serial port, in characters per second. The default value is determined by the particular platform. Current known values are 57600 for the BAN and 9600 for other devices.

consoleInactivityTime.name: consoleInactivityTime
consoleInactivityTime.description: The console inactivity time where after this number of minutes, the user is automatically logged out. A value of 0 disables the timer. The default is 30 minutes.
